'''ModelSim''' 是[[明導國際|明導國際]]<ref name="b1">[https://books.google.com/books?id=Eqgrqktkk1YC&pg=PA606&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false Handbook of Digital Techniques for High-Speed Design] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Eqgrqktkk1YC&pg=PA606&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false |date=20200811113253 }}, Pearson Education India, 01-Sep-2007</ref>提供的多语言 HDL 仿真环境，用于仿真诸如[[VHDL|VHDL]]。[[Verilog|Verilog]]和[[SystemC|SystemC]]之类的[[硬件描述语言|硬件描述语言]]，并包含一个内置的 C 调试器。<ref name="b2">[https://books.google.com/books?id=F-mTrH1NB4UC&pg=PA97&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false Reconfigurable Embedded Control Systems] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=F-mTrH1NB4UC&pg=PA97&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false |date=20200806001101 }}, Idea Group Inc (IGI), 30-Nov-2010</ref>ModelSim可以单独使用，也可以与[[Altera_Quartus|Intel Quartus Prime]]、[[Xilinx_ISE|Xilinx ISE]]或Xilinx Vivado等软件结合使用。<ref name="b5">[https://books.google.com/books?id=wUALmyy9YUcC&pg=PA41&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false Digital Hardware Design] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wUALmyy9YUcC&pg=PA41&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false |date=20200805233256 }}, Laxmi Publications, Ltd., 01-Sep-2008</ref>仿真的执行可以使用[[图形用户界面|图形用户界面]]（GUI）或自动[[脚本|脚本]]。<ref name="b7">[https://books.google.com/books?id=ljLBBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA17&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false Synthesizable VHDL Design for FPGAs] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ljLBBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA17&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false |date=20200811123322 }}, Springer Science & Business Media, 21-Oct-2013</ref>

== 版本 ==
Mentor HDL 仿真产品提供了多个版本，例如 ModelSim PE 和 Questa Sim。

Questa Sim 提供高性能和高级调试功能，而 ModelSim PE 是面向爱好者和学生的入门级模拟器。<ref name="b1"/>Questa Sim 用于数百万逻辑门的大型设计中，并在32位和64位的 [[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]] 和 Linux 上受支持。

通过 ''Link for ModelSim''，ModelSim 也可以与 [[MATLAB|MATLAB]]/[[Simulink|Simulink]] 一起使用。<ref name="b6">[https://books.google.com/books?id=cnkYRKhUwyEC&pg=PA849&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false Industrial Control Technology] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cnkYRKhUwyEC&pg=PA849&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false |date=20200810161437 }}, William Andrew, 12-Aug-2008</ref><ref name="b4">[https://books.google.com/books?id=pJSqZZmc9_oC&pg=PA168&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false Recent Advances in Modeling and Simulation Tools for Communication Networks and Services] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pJSqZZmc9_oC&pg=PA168&dq=ModelSim&hl=en&sa=X#v=onepage&q=ModelSim&f=false |date=20200810214840 }}, Springer Science & Business Media, 20-Sep-2007</ref>''Link for ModelSim'' 是 Simulink 和 ModelSim 之间的快速双向协同仿真接口。对于此类设计，MATLAB 提供了一个数值仿真工具箱，而 ModelSim 提供了用于验证设计的硬件实现和时序特性的工具。

== 语言支持 ==
ModelSim 使用统一的内核来仿真所有受支持的语言，调试嵌入式 C 代码的方法与 VHDL 或 Verilog 相同。<ref name="b1"/>

ModelSim 和 Questa Sim 产品支持以下语言的仿真，验证和调试：<ref name="b1"/>

* [[VHDL|VHDL]]
* [[Verilog|Verilog]]
* [[Verilog|Verilog]] 2001
* [[SystemVerilog|SystemVerilog]]
* [[PSL|PSL]]
* [[SystemC|SystemC]]

